reviewText: have seen these videos  several years ago. Born Yesterday is great, since it shows a naive woman in a relationship with a lobbyist, who is not only corrupt but abusive. to  see  someone that actually knows the US Constition and  the Bill of Rights is amazing, and the issue of buying and abusing senators sure hits what is presently going on today. moral of story EDUCATE, EDUCATE,EDUCATE  this is not over the top ,mealy moouth preachy messages , it;s happening now.  Mr Wrong is one of Ellen's gems.

reviewText: Great sit on the couch an do nothing but laugh movies. Each one as funny as the next.  My favorite of the three is Born Yesterday, but I liked the other two almost as much.  A great DVD to put in if you are home sick or just have day when you want to do nothing and relax and enjoy the day.  Of course you can watch one at a time, or if you are like me, an insomniac, it was a great DVD to help me through the night.dlp
